# JSON access, so without these the bot will save Reddit links as
# "Could Not Be Fetched". Create a free "script" app at
# https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps (redirect URI can be http://localhost).
# REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=...
# REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=...
